Euro Falls Versus Dollar; Trichet Says ECB to Monitor Developments Closely

-- B y   L u c y   M e a k i n
-- 
2011-05-05T12:35:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/euro-falls-versus-dollar-trichet-says-ecb-to-monitor-developments-closely.html
The euro weakened against the dollar
after European Central Bank President Jean-Claude Trichet said
policy makers will monitor developments “closely.”  The euro dropped 0.6 percent to $1.4741 as 1:34 p.m. in
 London , and slid 1.7 percent against the yen to 117.52.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucy Meakin in London at 
